Class rammWalker

  • java.lang.Object
    • rammBaseListener
      • rammWalker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener, rammListener

    public class rammWalker
extends rammBaseListener
    Rammwalker class extends the rammbaselistener generated by antlr. This class overrides the method provided by rammbaselistener and help in walking through generated abstract syantax tree.
